long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Adventure Dental takes players on an exciting journey through the world of oral health and dental challenges. Developed by Smile Studios, this educational and entertaining game combines adventure with dental care, offering players a unique and engaging experience.

Game Controls
Master the controls to navigate dental challenges:

Arrow Keys: Control character movement.
Spacebar: Interact with objects and characters.
Mouse: Use the mouse for specific interactions.
How to Play
Navigate Dental Challenges: Embark on a dental adventure, navigating through challenges related to oral hygiene and health.
Complete Mini-Games: Engage in mini-games that focus on dental care practices, such as brushing, flossing, and more.
Earn Rewards: Successfully completing challenges and mini-games earns rewards, encouraging positive dental habits.
Explore Dental Environments: Explore different dental environments, from the waiting room to the dentist’s chair, each with unique challenges.

# Play more games on the top-left menu.
